# For IPv4 hosts
127.0.0.1 localhost

# For IPv6 hosts
## https://unix.stackexchange.com/a/234447
::1     localhost
::1     ip6-localhost
::1     ip6-loopback
fe00::0 ip6-localnet
ff00::0 ip6-mcastprefix
ff02::1 ip6-allnodes
ff02::2 ip6-allrouters
ff02::3 ip6-allhosts

# Other possible hosts
## https://gist.github.com/ghoneycutt/e531984406b4b86ace687ea8958a6dc3
127.0.0.1 local localhost.localdomain localhost4 localhost4.localdomain4
255.255.255.255 broadcasthost
